# WeChat Cover Designer

Use `scripts/wechat_cover.py` as the stable CLI interface.

For WeChat covers, generate `1645x700` (`2.35:1`) images with:

```bash
python3 scripts/wechat_cover.py --input input.png --output cover.png --title "标题" --platform wechat
```

Follow `references/cover-style.md` for visual changes. Preserve the warm editorial style, dark gradient, large Chinese title, and green accent highlight.

Keep `SKILL.md` for Codex compatibility, but do not make the project depend on Codex-specific runtime features.
